# Normalize line endings: auto-detect text, store as LF in repo and check
# out as LF. Prevents Windows checkouts from generating phantom CRLF diffs.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary asset hints (auto-detection covers these too, but being explicit
# avoids accidental text munging on edge tools).
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ico  binary
*.icns binary
*.gif  binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf  binary
*.otf  binary
